  description: "Ninh B\xECnh l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\u1ED3ng
    b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng H\u1ED3ng \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam. Sau
    khi s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh, Ninh B\xECnh v\u1EABn
    l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh c\xF3 v\u1ECB tr\xED quan tr\u1ECDng \u1EDF c\u1EEDa
    ng\xF5 ph\xEDa nam c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng H\u1ED3ng, v\u1EDBi
    \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng g\u1ED3m n\xFAi \u0111\xE1 v\xF4i,
    \u0111\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng v\xE0 v\xF9ng ven bi\u1EC3n. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh
    l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Ninh B\xECnh. T\u1EC9nh n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi
    nhi\u1EC1u danh lam th\u1EAFng c\u1EA3nh nh\u01B0 Qu\u1EA7n th\u1EC3 danh th\u1EAFng
    Tr\xE0ng An, Ch\xF9a B\xE1i \u0110\xEDnh v\xE0 Tam C\u1ED1c \u2013 B\xEDch \u0110\u1ED9ng.\n\nNinh
    B\xECnh n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi c\xE1c \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n nh\u01B0 Th\u1ECBt
    d\xEA n\xFAi Ninh B\xECnh v\xE0 C\u01A1m ch\xE1y Ninh B\xECnh, l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng
    m\xF3n \u0103n g\u1EAFn li\u1EC1n v\u1EDBi du l\u1ECBch c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1ECBa
    ph\u01B0\u01A1ng.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, Ninh B\xECnh l\xE0 v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t
    gi\xE0u truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng l\u1ECBch s\u1EED, t\u1EEBng l\xE0 kinh \u0111\xF4
    c\u1EE7a n\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0110\u1EA1i C\u1ED3 Vi\u1EC7t d\u01B0\u1EDBi tri\u1EC1u
    Nh\xE0 \u0110inh v\xE0 Ti\u1EC1n L\xEA t\u1EA1i C\u1ED1 \u0111\xF4 Hoa L\u01B0.
    C\xE1c l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng t\u1EA1i Hoa L\u01B0 v\xE0 nhi\u1EC1u
    di t\xEDch l\u1ECBch s\u1EED trong t\u1EC9nh th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n r\xF5 n\xE9t
    gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB v\u0103n h\xF3a v\xE0 l\u1ECBch s\u1EED l\xE2u \u0111\u1EDDi
    c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t n\xE0y."
  desSatNhap: "Ba t\u1EC9nh H\xE0 Nam, Nam \u0110\u1ECBnh v\xE0 Ninh B\xECnh s\xE1p
    nh\u1EADp th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi l\u1EA5y t\xEAn l\xE0 Ninh B\xECnh,
    ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c t\u1EEB th\xE1ng 6/2025. T\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 di\u1EC7n
    t\xEDch 3.942,6km vu\xF4ng \r                                                        
    , d\xE2n s\u1ED1 kho\u1EA3ng 3,8 - 4,4 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, trung t\xE2m
    h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i khu v\u1EF1c th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Ninh B\xECnh
    hi\u1EC7n nay. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 b\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111i chi\u1EBFn l\u01B0\u1EE3c
    nh\u1EB1m t\u1EA1o ra kh\xF4ng gian ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n kinh t\u1EBF di s\u1EA3n,
    c\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p v\xE0 bi\u1EC3n m\u1EA1nh h\u01A1n."
